
Version 0.2:

* Added the search capability now you can find all your movies in the pile
  - it filters out when you type in the search box, a fast way to search
* Added a key shortcut function, which now allows you to press the delete
  key to delete the selected movie(s). Soon more shortcuts will be added/
Version 0.3 (2018):
* http://www.omdbapi.com/ API now requires an API Key, a default API key is
now added
* README file contains the Ubuntu dependencies required for the build

